{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"534b936b4e","title":"在修改《对于战后国际形势中几个基本问题的解释》一文时加写的一段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f5808f8974","index":0,"year":1947,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"534b936b4e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d20738c862","name":"世界形势","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8798b0c743","type":"paragraph","text":"在修改《对于战后国际形势中几个基本问题的解释》一文时","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"534b936b4e"},{"id":"2d9ad4441e","type":"paragraph","text":"加写的一段话","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"534b936b4e"},{"id":"c48d679027","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年1月1日）","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"534b936b4e"},{"id":"70d8ef049f","type":"paragraph","text":"总而言之，第二次世界大战后，一切都变了，并正在继续变在人民方面，是变得如此坚强，如此有觉悟，有组织，有决心，有信心。在反动派方面，则已变得如此横蛋碧薇，但又如此外强中干，众叛亲离，对于前途完全失去信心。可以预断，三年至五年后的中国与世界，其面自将比现时大不相同。全党同志与全中国人民，都应当为一个新中国与新世界而坚决奋斗","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"534b936b4e"}],"page":{"id":"9e6bfacf3e","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"534b936b4e","start":345,"end":345}}}},"__N_SSG":true}